Actress Yvonne De Carlo is 64. Country singer Conway Twitty is 55.
Conductor Seiji Ozawa is 53. Comedian-actress Lily Tomlin is 49.
Singer Barry Gibb is 42.
   Thought for today: ``History is the autobiography of a madman.''
_ Alexander Herzen, Russian author (1812-1870).
